   Cheruiyot, Duncan; Van den Berg, Johnnie, North West Univ, Unit Environm Sci \& Management, ZA-2520 Potchefstroom, South Africa.
   Pickett, John A., Rothamsted Res, Dept Biol Chem, Harpenden AL5 2JQ, Herts, England.},
